## 🔍 安全扫描

### 依赖扫描

```bash
# safety - Python 依赖扫描
pip install safety
safety check
safety check --full-report

# npm audit - Node.js 依赖扫描
npm audit
npm audit fix

# Snyk - 综合扫描
npm install -g snyk
snyk auth
snyk test
snyk monitor
```

### 代码扫描

```bash
# bandit - Python 安全扫描
pip install bandit
bandit -r app/
bandit -r app/ -f html -o bandit-report.html

# ESLint security - JavaScript 安全扫描
npm install eslint-plugin-security
# .eslintrc.js
plugins: ['security']
extends: ['plugin:security/recommended']
```

### 容器扫描

```bash
# trivy - 容器漏洞扫描
docker run -v /var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock \
  aquasec/trivy image myapp:latest

# docker scan
docker scan myapp:latest
```

